{"tid":859312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[克霖醒] 係西九嘅連登仔一定要提名龍心 同投佢一票","createTime":"2018-10-12T11:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T04:38:03.000Z","uid":51620,"like":36,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4dc9b8913fa29ceba567ea84f0f9f2589933f8","tid":859312,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/menclub.hk/videos/10159331983875385/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmenclub.hk%2Fvideos%2F10159331983875385%2F&d=F8hzy82cj0pziVwnC6BPNviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d4cac90c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/menclub.hk/videos/10159331983875385/</a><br />\n<br />\n林克霖五年來創出「王小虎」、「猴子農」等多個角色。有人認為他人格分裂，事實上連他自己都不知道究竟哪個才是他「自己」，更不知道自己是不是「正常」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181012/58783867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F58783867&d=F8hzy82cj0pziVwnC6BPNviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e7f7ffec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F58783867&h=f8b5ec42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181012/58783867</a><br />\n<br />\n自稱「龍心」的網絡紅人林克霖，於蘋果節目《你問我答》正式宣傳參選立法會九龍西補選。雖然未知是否夠提名票入閘，但就已率先點評已交表的參選人。<br />\n<br />\n龍心指在上節目前抽幾分鐘時間看《維基百科》，稱馮檢基無能力統籌區內各方勢力及警察，呼籲他將選票全數過到自己名下，自己可以考慮付薪請他工作。對於劉小麗，龍心指上周在街上見到她，欲上前對話，但對方一直重複「六點鐘約咗人」，拒絕與自己對話，「連同市民對答能力都冇。」<br />\n<br />\n至於另一位已報名參選的陳凱欣，龍心就與她爭奪「風之子」的名號，稱自己才是被「山竹」吹出來參選，並即場播出自己早前拍攝、拿起樹葉跑步的短片作為「證據」。<br />\n<br />\n目前已交表報名參選人為馮檢基、劉小麗及陳凱欣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20181011/large/1539259797_dfec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20181011%2Flarge%2F1539259797_dfec.jpg&h=4f618aa3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa58659973ba067b7ea1ba9dbbca7f34417daaef","tid":859312,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d85cbf34a47d13d7dfac653184566b455314e8","tid":859312,"uid":147047,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:11:26.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"833a35fc90202e039f7ddfdede0b978820644e75","tid":859312,"uid":208722,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"10d2b65c14e756ee970e1d1b63ca4659af4007bd","tid":859312,"uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a3d85cbf34a47d13d7dfac653184566b455314e8","tid":859312,"uid":147047,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:11:26.000Z","msg":"十卜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740e847becd8eb1aa19e29a7283b1bd06c13f942","tid":859312,"uid":22888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a7368a487414b83f6b89ebf6e89ee4995b24e0","tid":859312,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4ced62f51be64b900d46a26495aae92d4704c17","tid":859312,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab75f9f1344a255adeb12a517551a2a4080d2ee1","tid":859312,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:37:52.00